Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsume, Ishimura.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, once the exam's over, the rest is easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.99,0:02:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Fishing, maybe?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.91,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me in on that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasada...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.42,0:02:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's friend gave him these.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go together.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,An art museum?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.27,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, the exam's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer's come again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.45,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.34,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back, Takashi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.80,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? It's from a class reunion.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From elementary school.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about those days.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so old now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess everyone else is, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss being a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.95,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, there's something \Nthat's been bothering me a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you hear me out, Takashi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.38,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, a bunch of us good friends exchanged presents.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.88,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody said that they would make something.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all so excited.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We all sang around in a circle,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.35,0:04:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ended up with \NKuriyama{**-san}'s handmade cookies.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.31,0:04:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{**-san} got the pressed flower cards I made.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.48,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But... she looked so unhappy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"I didn't want something like this!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're no fair, Touko{**-chan}!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Give me back my cookies!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.28,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've apologized.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.92,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she or anybody else \Nremembers it, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.72,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{**-san} moved away, after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see her again.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to talk about what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think that if I saw that she was doing well,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.57,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing that's been bothering me would just vanish.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.00,0:05:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have any good memories of my childhood.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.17,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about going to an art museum?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.59,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked you to come.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.89,0:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think Sasada said \Nthere was a good ramen place nearby.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.89,0:05:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ramen? Ramen? Ramen?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sneak into my bag again.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said you weren't!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, I'm going, I'm going! I'm going!{said four times?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ra... ramen...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.83,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here and watch the house!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.13,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Now my days are full of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!{unsubbed line after}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hold my breath for ten minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's useless!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.98,0:06:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not useless!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I guess it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.57,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I heard you found something cool?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a big bug.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being invisible is honestly really useless.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humans just walk past me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like the seasons.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that summer, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was one person...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who could see me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's watching.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with that branch?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.79,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just toss it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How arrogant! How rude!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.05,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those insensitive lower organisms \Ncan't even sense a noble being like me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Nose hair!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crappy day.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.77,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be something that could cheer me up.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the liar's coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, the liar's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get close to him, you'll turn into a liar too!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally will!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.91,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.99,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoo-shoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mocking their companions at such a young age.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How ugly.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that rock came from the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of lie you'd tell, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Noisy brats.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, say something!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bugs!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... he looked right at me...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can see me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can't see spirits.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.34,0:08:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody can see me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a rude kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't forget this!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For every day after that, I chased him,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lied in ambush,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and scared him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He always ran away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was all, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.51,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it was kind of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.43,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, where is he today?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he transferred, didn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard he's creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He tells weird lies.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he can see monsters just to get attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.32,0:09:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he doesn't have any parents \Nand nobody wants him, so he keeps transferring.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's always alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's always alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just because he can see us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I made an elephant today!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.01,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did a handstand!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got scared! You were scared, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the first time he's spoken to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.87,0:10:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you care about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.87,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bored?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!{added stutter}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be passing by.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody as important as me \Nhas lots of stuff to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about somebody like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nose hair!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look at that! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.27,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to live around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up about the ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Natsume?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're spacing out.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.41,0:12:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you hungry, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.46,0:12:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My relatives passed me from one house to another.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.80,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I don't remember exactly where I was.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one with the problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I need you to take him next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.48,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the deal!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.53,0:12:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... you, well... well...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.04,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be living at my brother's house \Nstarting next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid's got college exams this year.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.96,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And... oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you this coat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a bit big, but that's no problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think badly of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For, well, everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of dusty.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.21,0:13:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And just when we'd finally spoken.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be nice to some human kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I'll scare him like always.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I scare him, he might talk to me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get that coat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}He's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle gave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.54,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}All right, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.93,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm soaked!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that for?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shoot! I didn't mean to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.69,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.36,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did I do to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.28,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate you all!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.87,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was last day he took this path.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.21,0:15:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It felt like he was taking \Nthe long way around to school.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.85,0:15:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think he'll listen to me anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He won't see me anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.32,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's alone again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a kitty.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.81,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.95,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell kind of nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.96,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks so kind...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's warm.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.05,0:16:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to stay by him forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to be you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.10,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be alone, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.08,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a spirit, so I don't understand humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.16,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's sad to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If nothing else, I know that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.22,0:17:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A few days ago, he was taken far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's that woman?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her lips and nails are bright red.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that man's eyes keep shifting around.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a kid your age.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it. You'll get used to it soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a fun family.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.34,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never saw him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So what if I'm alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's much better to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do those humans always \Nwant to be with each other?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What pretty flowers!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.00,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Something touched my hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. That's scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.55,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how long am I supposed to \Ntake care of your mother?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.06,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick of this? {You can't...}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an ugly, twisted face.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.15,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really hate humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just take care of her?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.36,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish they'd all just disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate them!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate them all!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.66,0:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ugly things that only think about themselves...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd all disappear!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it's dangerous to go under that tree.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know everything, \Nbut something scary's supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate cats!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time has stopped for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's he doing now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.60,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With his kind smile, and his sad wish...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he smiling?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know how many seasons it's been,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I've never forgotten.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.59,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always remembered.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bothering me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.59,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We said goodbye in such a strange way.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I could only get mad at others,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, I think I understand your kindness.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.81,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure he's met another kind soul...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if he can smile like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember this smell.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.62,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Natsume Takashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.64,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You met her, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.85,0:21:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I had one, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.82,0:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want to make a stop somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, there's somebody I want to find.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.54,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old friend, \Nbut I don't know if I can see them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just head home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.00,0:21:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.84,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.84,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good time!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.93,0:22:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.15,0:22:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.44,0:22:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there's somebody you want to see,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then you're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.09,0:24:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There are demons who remember \Nmy grandfather here in this house?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.30,0:24:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they all came because they remembered him.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.26,0:24:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather was never able to see demons.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.14,0:24:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people see them even if they don't want to.
